| `gemma-4-12b-qat` | Gemma-4-12B-it-QAT | UD-Q4_K_XL | 6.3 GB + 168 MB | `/models/gemma-4-12b-qat/` | on-demand | Synthese LLM1b (Phase 1b) + Repair (Phase 3b) |
